summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Lighting; accepting the offer of Robert G. Stark and Mary Ann Stark, his wife, to purchase certain City (Lighting Department) property in Sections 17 and 18, Township 27 North, Range 5 East, W.M., in Snohomish County, Washington, subject to certain reservations, and authorizing execution and delivery of a quitclaim deed thereto.
